name: Pelanggan Report
query:
select

`tabMaster Pelanggan`.nama_pelanggan as "Nama Pelanggan:data:20",
`tabMaster Pelanggan`.tipe_pelanggan as "Tipe Pelanggan:data:6",
`tabMaster Pelanggan`.total_belanja as "Total Belanja:20",
`tabMaster Pelanggan`.total_point as "Total Point: 20",
`tabMaster Pelanggan`.join_date as "Join Date:Date:100"

from `tabMaster Pelanggan` order by `tabMaster Pelanggan`.join_date
